   <TITLE>curvature2d</TITLE>
   <TYPE>SIP Toolbox</TYPE>
   <DATE>February 2004</DATE>
   <SHORT_DESCRIPTION name="curvature2d">Curvature of a surface or image</SHORT_DESCRIPTION>
   <CALLING_SEQUENCE>
      <CALLING_SEQUENCE_ITEM>Output = curvature2d(Input)</CALLING_SEQUENCE_ITEM>
   </CALLING_SEQUENCE>
   <DESCRIPTION>
   <P>
 "curvature2d" calculates the curvature of an intensity  image or
 surface represented as a 2D matrix. It currently uses a simple finite
 difference scheme. </P>
   </DESCRIPTION>
